    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Concessio in <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">emphyteusim</rs> ripę
                            <rs key="#Rivers">flumins</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Rivers #Landed_possessions #Mills"
                            ref="#places/3584">Savennę</placeName> ad faciendum <rs key="#Mills"
                            >molendinum</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terrarum</rs> ad ipsam
                        ripam pertinentium, ad <rs key="#Roads">stratam</rs> antiquam, seu voltam
                        eius, facta a <persName><name ref="Giseltruda">Giseltruda</name></persName>
                        filia <persName><name ref="Ursus">Ursonis</name></persName> relicta
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus de Benedicto">Petri de
                            Benedicto</name></persName> et ab <persName><name ref="Ildeberga"
                                >Ildeberga</name></persName> filia Giseltrudę cum consensu tutoris
                        et <persName key="#Judge" ref="#people/92"><name
                            ref="Petrus iudex Nonantulensis">Petri</name></persName> <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs> Romani in <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/47">Nonantula</orgName>,
                        favore <persName><name ref="Anastasia/Vitarella">Anastasię vocatur Vitarellę</name></persName> filie
                        <persName><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName>, filiorum et heredum. Actum […], rog. 
                        <persName><name ref="Rainbertus">Rimperti</name></persName> <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs>, 1061,
                        domini Henrici Henrici filii V, XI kalendas novembris, indictione XV.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>Mezzetti, <foreign>Le carte</foreign>, vol. 2, doc. 34 (in preparazione).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mezzetti, per la sua edizione delle carte di Pomposa, si rifà in parte a una
                    serie di regesti realizzati da Bacchini nel XVIII secolo (Bacchini,
                        <foreign>Regesto Cronologico</foreign> (sec. XVIII in.), cc. 22v, da A
                    perduto).</p>
            </div>
